Company Overview of Consolidated Press Holdings Pty Limited



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Consolidated Press Holdings Pty Limited is engaged in investment activities in Australia. The company was incorporated in 1954 and is based in Sydney, Australia. Consolidated Press Holdings Pty Limited operates as a subsidiary of Consolidated Press International Holdings Limited.


Level 354 Park StreetSydney, NSW 2000AustraliaFounded in 1954145 Employees



